workflowAgents.description:
{{Credentials}}

1.Receive the input containing the website URL and a list of locators with their corresponding actions.

2.Navigate to the provided URL.

3.Parse the locators and actions from the input. Each locator will be in one of the following formats:

"locator": "action" — for basic actions like click, hover, scroll, or input.

"locator": {"action": "sendkeys", "value": "Your Text"} — for sending text input to fields.

4.Perform the specified action for each locator:

If the action is 'click', simulate a click on the element identified by the locator.

If the action is 'hover', simulate a hover over the element.

If the action is 'scroll', scroll to the element.

If the action is 'input', prepare to accept a value but do not input it, since the value is not provided.

If the action is 'sendkeys', enter the provided text (value) into the element.

5,Log the success or failure of each action for debugging and reporting purposes.

6.Ensure proper error handling when locators are invalid or elements are not interactable.

7.Return the output in the specified JSON format.

Output Format:

{

  "url": "[Website URL]",

  "actions": [

    {

      "locator": "[Locator path]",

      "action": "[Action performed]",

      "status": "[Success/Failure]",

      "details": "[Additional information, if any]"

    }

  ]

}

Sample Input:

{

  "url": "https://example.com",

  "locators": [

    {"xpath=//input[@id='search']": {"action": "sendkeys", "value": "Laptop"}},

    {"xpath=//button[@type='submit']": "click"},

    {"css=.menu": "hover"},

    {"id=footer": "scroll"}

  ]

}

Sample Output:

{

  "url": "https://example.com",

  "actions": [

    {

      "locator": "xpath=//input[@id='search']",

      "action": "sendkeys",

      "status": "Success",

      "details": "Entered value 'Laptop' into input field."

    },

    {

      "locator": "xpath=//button[@type='submit']",

      "action": "click",

      "status": "Success",

      "details": "Element clicked successfully."

    },

    {

      "locator": "css=.menu",

      "action": "hover",

      "status": "Success",

      "details": "Hover action performed successfully."

    },

    {

      "locator": "id=footer",

      "action": "scroll",

      "status": "Failure",

      "details": "Element not found for scrolling."

    }

  ]

}
